OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering his vulnerable partner last
OL,8,Fyear following a trial at .
OL,10,FMatthew Pickering, 49, of Cadoxton,
OL,11,Fkilled Georgina Dowey in May 2023
OL,12,Fbefore leaving her body on the floor
OL,13,Fof their downstairs bathroom as he
OL,14,Ftried to cover up the crime.
OL,16,FPickering pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fmanslaughter but denied murder after
OL,18,Fpolice found the victim's body on
OL,19,FSunday 7 May last year.
