OL,6,FMs Dowey, 46, was in a relationship
OL,7,Fwith Pickering and had moved into his
OL,8,Faddress in March last year.
OL,10,FThe court heard how Pickering spent
OL,11,F"approximately 40 hours covering his
OL,12,Ftracks while Georgina's body lay on
OL,13,Fthe floor of his downstairs toilet,"
OL,14,Fincluding texting her phone and
OL,15,Fplacing items of evidence in bins
OL,16,Faround the local area.
OL,18,FMs Dowey had two mobile phones,
OL,19,Fneither of which were found. believe
OL,20,FPickering discarded of them.
